Subject: RFP 2026-S04 Summer Classroom Repainting Roosevelt Elementary
Date: Fri, 12 Jun 2026 09:30:00 -0500

Saint Paul Public Schools invites proposals for the summer repainting of
22 classrooms, 4 hallways, and 2 common areas at Roosevelt Elementary.

Work window: July 20, 2026 through August 15, 2026.
Estimated value: $28,000 - $42,000.
Response due by July 1, 2026 at 4:00 PM CDT.

No performance bond required for contracts under $50,000.
Prevailing wage applies (SPPS board policy).

Scope:
  - Patch nail holes and minor drywall damage
  - Two coats interior latex eggshell, "or equal" to Sherwin-Williams
    ProMar 200 or Benjamin Moore Ultra Spec 500
  - Trim & doors: semi-gloss, contractor's choice of manufacturer
  - Ceilings: flat white, contractor's choice
  - District-approved alternates may be submitted at any time

Exclusions: HVAC, electrical, plumbing, flooring, window replacement.

Bid package: https://www.spps.org/cms/lib/MN01910242/Centricity/Domain/27/2026-S04.pdf

Questions: purchasing@spps.org
